data.text:
Pizza Hut Express offers the classic American pizzeria in personal pan pizzas crafted for the on-the-go student. If pizza isn’t your dish; pasta, wings, and bread sticks are also available.

Academic year hours

Location

Pizza Hut Express is located in the University Union, Bldg 30A, next to the Sushi Place. Map and directions

Menu & nutrition

View Pizza Hut’s nutrition information. Check out the NAUgo app to view the menu.
